The Intense Integrated Chinese Textbook Lore

In the Integrated Chinese Textbook, there are six characters with a love square between four of the characters.

The Main Four

Wang Peng/王朋

Wang Peng is a Chinese freshman from Beijing. He has quickly adapted to American college life and likes to play and watch sports.

Relationship to Amy Lee/李友: Friends, seems to have an interest in her, offers to help her out a lot in Chinese.

Relationship to Winston Gore/高文中: Roommates, opposite interests.

Relationship to Baek Yeung Ae/白英爱: Friends, goes out to dinner with her but doesn't seem that interested in her.

Amy Lee/李友

Amy Lee is a fellow New Yorker. In addition to her major in college, she has to take a Chinese class.

Relationship to Winston Gore/高文中: Doesn't really interact with him, he called her once to tell her they had a test the next day.

Relationship to Baek Yeung Ae/白英爱: Friends, gets upset when she mentions Wang Peng in class once, appears to be jealous when she hears she invited Wang Peng to dinner once.

Relationship to Wang Peng/王朋: Meets him on the first day of class, becomes good friends with him, gets Chinese help from him, constantly compliments his Chinese skills.

Winston Gore/高文中

Winston Gore is from England, but his parents work in the US. He enjoys singing, dancing, and sleeping. He also loves to eat Chinese food.

Relationship to Amy Lee/李友: Doesn't really interact with her, called her once to tell her they had a test the next day.

Relationship to Baek Yeung Ae/白英爱: Interested in her, invites her out often, disappointed when she invites Wang Peng to their hangout.

Relationship to Wang Peng/王朋: Roomates, opposite interests, seems jealous of Baek Yeung Ae's affection towards Wang Peng.

Baek Yeung Ae/白英爱

Baek Yeung Ae is from Seoul, Korea.

Relationship to Amy Lee/李友: Friends, exposed her frienship with Wang Pang in class once.

Relationship to Winston Gore/高文中: Friends, doesn't seem to know that he's attracted to her, treated him to dinner for his birthday.

Relationship to Wang Peng/王朋: Interested in him, called him handsome and cool, asked him out to dinner, invites him to hangout.

Supplementary Characters

Jenny Gore/高小音

Winston Gore's sister. She graduated college and works as a librarian.

Chang Xiaoliang/常老师

The Main Four's Teacher. Originally from China, she has been teaching in the US for the past ten years.
